DUET(1)                      DOCUMENTATION                      DUET(1)

NAME
     duet - minimalist dual pane terminal file manager

SYNOPSIS
     duet

DESCRIPTION
     duet is a dual pane terminal file manager.

     Left pane navigates filesystem. Right pane shows live preview:
     directories (contents), text files (first screenful), binaries
     (sanitized dump).

QUICK REFERENCE
     navigate          (hjkl, arrows)
     parent dir        (h, <)
     enter/open        (l, >, Enter)
     top/bottom        (g, G)
     hidden files      (.)
     home              (~)
     fuzzy find        (Tab, /)
     shell             (!)
     quit              (q, Ctrl-C)

     Preview updates instantly. Directories blue, executables green.

BUILD
     gcc -o duet duet.c
     make

INSTALL
     make install

